00:17:18,760 --> 00:17:21,640
are cheaper than grains,

292
00:17:21,640 --> 00:17:23,830
fabrics, carriages and horses,

293
00:17:26,470 --> 00:17:28,420
but not friendships.

294
00:17:30,560 --> 00:17:32,310
What a tragedy!

295
00:17:39,950 --> 00:17:41,400
Mr. Xie. Mr. Xie.

296
00:17:41,400 --> 00:17:42,240
Are you alright?

297
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:44,160
Mr. Xie,

298
00:17:45,110 --> 00:17:46,420
we should go back.

299
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:56,850
Her skills

300
00:17:57,800 --> 00:17:59,200
aren’t too bad

301
00:18:00,110 --> 00:18:02,360
and her look is slightly better.

302
00:18:05,110 --> 00:18:06,760
But she doesn’t look like Li Zheng

303
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:09,120
or me.

304
00:18:10,070 --> 00:18:10,880
Does she

305
00:18:12,470 --> 00:18:15,000
look more like her other grandmother?

306
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,280
Ma’am, Ma’am.

307
00:18:16,950 --> 00:18:17,850
Ma’am,

308
00:18:18,280 --> 00:18:20,530
she probably resembles her father.

309
00:18:23,520 --> 00:18:24,870
That makes sense.

310
00:18:25,830 --> 00:18:27,080
I’ve never seen him.

311
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:28,160
Perhaps you can

312
00:18:29,280 --> 00:18:30,740
introduce him to me some other day.

313
00:18:32,710 --> 00:18:33,480
Ma’am,

314
00:18:34,040 --> 00:18:35,600
may I know your name?

315
00:18:37,190 --> 00:18:38,230
Call me Duan Jiuniang.

316
00:18:41,830 --> 00:18:42,760
Who are you?

317
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:44,550
Where are your parents?

318
00:18:45,470 --> 00:18:46,740
My name is Wu Chuchu.

319
00:18:48,110 --> 00:18:49,200
My parents...

320
00:18:51,470 --> 00:18:52,510
They died?

321
00:18:54,760 --> 00:18:57,190
Well, that happens.

322
00:18:57,190 --> 00:18:58,230
Look at me.

323
00:18:58,470 --> 00:18:59,780
I have no family.

324
00:19:00,710 --> 00:19:02,590
And my lover

325
00:19:05,040 --> 00:19:06,480
always acts against me.

326
00:19:19,230 --> 00:19:21,230
You must’ve got your temper

327
00:19:21,230 --> 00:19:22,780
from your grandfather.

328
00:19:26,310 --> 00:19:27,650
Am I right?

329
00:19:34,280 --> 00:19:35,420
Answer me.

330
00:19:36,710 --> 00:19:38,090
Why are you so quiet?

331
00:19:39,950 --> 00:19:41,360
Say something!

332
00:19:42,280 --> 00:19:44,000
Say it!

333
00:20:02,280 --> 00:20:03,400
What happened?

334
00:20:05,590 --> 00:20:07,400
Are you having a relapse?

335
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:09,110
Let Mr. Bai check you

336
00:20:09,110 --> 00:20:10,140
in case you...

337
00:20:11,310 --> 00:20:12,020
Mr. Bai.

338
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:21,940
Mr. Bai, what are you doing?

339
00:20:25,920 --> 00:20:28,080
Zichen, help him up.

340
00:20:28,560 --> 00:20:29,520
Get up, Mr. Bai.

341
00:20:30,040 --> 00:20:31,670
I made a mistake.

342
00:20:32,110 --> 00:20:33,350
Please punish me.

343
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:35,260
What do you mean?

344
00:20:36,070 --> 00:20:37,830
Demons dragged Mr. Xie’s friend out

345
00:20:37,830 --> 00:20:40,110
from the fire,

346
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:41,680
tortured him in cold blood

347
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:42,470
in public

348
00:20:42,470 --> 00:20:43,670
and twisted the facts.

349
00:20:44,520 --> 00:20:47,070
They disguised as civilians

350
00:20:47,070 --> 00:20:48,220
and had no mercy on him.

351
00:20:48,800 --> 00:20:50,470
I couldn’t see him

352
00:20:50,470 --> 00:20:51,740
being tortured to death,

353
00:20:52,280 --> 00:20:52,980
so I...

354
00:20:55,520 --> 00:20:58,000
I ended his life.

355
00:21:00,350 --> 00:21:01,200
Mr. Bai, you...

356
00:21:02,310 --> 00:21:03,770
You killed his friend?

357
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:05,260
I...

358
00:21:09,190 --> 00:21:09,890
Xie Yun...

359
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:13,740
Zichen,

360
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:16,290
calm down.

361
00:21:22,950 --> 00:21:23,660
Mr. Bai,

362
00:21:24,710 --> 00:21:25,470
please get up.

363
00:21:34,880 --> 00:21:35,680
Come to think of it,

364
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:39,440
were there the one I was looking for,

365
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:44,160
Mr. Bai was sending a message,

366
00:21:44,160 --> 00:21:45,600
telling her not to walk into the trap.

367
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:48,540
On top of that,

368
00:21:50,350 --> 00:21:52,780
Chenfei was in excruciating pain.

369
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:56,780
He was hoping for a quick death.

370
00:22:00,230 --> 00:22:01,450
I didn’t have the heart to do it,

371
00:22:04,470 --> 00:22:06,380
and Mr. Bai actually did him a favor.

372
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:12,200
I owe you

373
00:22:12,680 --> 00:22:13,940
and your friend my life.

374
00:22:14,560 --> 00:22:16,680
Whatever you need me
to do in the future,

375
00:22:16,680 --> 00:22:18,440
I’ll do it at all costs.

376
00:22:21,430 --> 00:22:22,020
Never mind.

377
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:31,280
Zichen,

378
00:22:32,590 --> 00:22:33,270
is there any liquor?

379
00:22:34,110 --> 00:22:34,610
Liquor?

380
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:15,040
Chenfei,

381
00:24:17,190 --> 00:24:18,780
I swear I’ll find Fei.

382
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:23,760
I’m Xie,

383
00:24:23,760 --> 00:24:24,680
named Meimei,

384
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:26,160
also known as the Optimistic Man.

385
00:24:27,070 --> 00:24:28,060
You are...

386
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:30,390
Xie Meimei?

387
00:24:34,070 --> 00:24:35,390
Weed Spirit?

388
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:49,410
You’re awake,

389
00:24:51,310 --> 00:24:51,920
Fei!

390
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:55,810
I think I heard Xie Yun calling me.

391
00:24:58,310 --> 00:25:00,430
I know you’re worried about him.

392
00:25:00,430 --> 00:25:01,590
Just relax.

393
00:25:01,590 --> 00:25:04,310
I saw him leaving first that day.

394
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:08,100
That’s a relief.

395
00:25:31,470 --> 00:25:33,000
-Xie Yun.
-Mr. Xie.

396
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:34,230
There you are!

397
00:25:34,230 --> 00:25:35,990
You were out all night.
Haven’t you found anything?

398
00:25:57,950 --> 00:25:58,520
Fei,

399
00:25:59,470 --> 00:26:01,020
are you still alive?

400
00:26:17,470 --> 00:26:19,260
Head means you’re safe

401
00:26:20,830 --> 00:26:21,520
and tail...

402
00:26:24,190 --> 00:26:26,100
-Open up!
-Open it!

403
00:26:33,350 --> 00:26:34,090
Lord,

404
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:36,130
Blessed Dog’s men have withdrawn.

405
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:39,190
Found anything?

406
00:26:39,190 --> 00:26:39,950
No.

407
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:42,470
(Stable as Mount Tai)

408
00:26:42,470 --> 00:26:45,190
Qiu Tianjin bit more than he could chew.

409
00:26:46,070 --> 00:26:47,160
And look what happened.

410
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:49,830
No one is left.

411
00:26:49,830 --> 00:26:51,310
The gate is closed

412
00:26:51,310 --> 00:26:52,070
and under close watch

413
00:26:52,070 --> 00:26:54,280
by the local government.

414
00:26:54,280 --> 00:26:56,230
Given that they managed to escape

415
00:26:56,230 --> 00:26:57,680
and lie low for so long,

416
00:26:58,310 --> 00:27:00,230
they must be something.

417
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:04,080
(Stable as Mount Tai)
Ignore others.

418
00:27:04,080 --> 00:27:05,210
(Stable as Mount Tai)

419
00:27:05,230 --> 00:27:07,200
(Stable as Mount Tai)
Just focus on our own search.

420
00:27:07,590 --> 00:27:08,880
Don’t forget

421
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:10,680
what we’re here for.

422
00:27:11,560 --> 00:27:12,350
Yes.

423
00:27:21,310 --> 00:27:22,350
-Negative.
-Let’s go.

424
00:27:22,350 --> 00:27:23,520
Search the next one.

425
00:27:26,760 --> 00:27:28,040
What’s happening?

426
00:27:28,110 --> 00:27:29,160
Lord has ordered us

427
00:27:29,160 --> 00:27:31,400
to focus on our own search.

428
00:27:45,110 --> 00:27:46,400
Jiachen, what’s the status?

429
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:47,830
Timber Wolf’s men
are doing their search.

430
00:27:47,830 --> 00:27:49,000
Tell us the details.

431
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:51,190
Timber Wolf and Blessed Dog

432
00:27:51,190 --> 00:27:52,310
are checking all places

433
00:27:52,310 --> 00:27:53,470
separately

434
00:27:53,470 --> 00:27:54,640
whether they’ve been searched

435
00:27:54,640 --> 00:27:56,070
by the other group or not.

436
00:27:56,070 --> 00:27:58,400
They aren’t exactly friends.

437
00:27:59,230 --> 00:28:01,490
But their focus is different.

438
00:28:02,310 --> 00:28:02,990
What do you mean?

439
00:28:03,590 --> 00:28:05,800
Blessed Dog focuses more
on women and children,

440
00:28:06,350 --> 00:28:08,640
especially boys, not girls.

441
00:28:10,310 --> 00:28:11,920
That means they’re looking for

442
00:28:11,920 --> 00:28:13,110
Miss Wu

443
00:28:13,110 --> 00:28:14,330
or Mr. Wu.

444
00:28:15,950 --> 00:28:17,070
What about Timber Wolf’s men?

445
00:28:17,070 --> 00:28:19,000
They match people with sketches

446
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:20,700
and check the names on the registration.

447
00:28:21,610 --> 00:28:22,850
They pay more attention to men.

448
00:28:24,110 --> 00:28:24,950
I knew it.

449
00:28:26,310 --> 00:28:27,060
What?

450
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:29,110
You know what I mean.

451
00:28:29,430 --> 00:28:31,070
Shen Tianshu isn’t
looking for Wu Chuchu,

452
00:28:31,070 --> 00:28:31,810
but you.

453
00:28:36,470 --> 00:28:38,110
How long will they be here?

454
00:28:38,110 --> 00:28:39,280
About ten minutes.

455
00:28:39,280 --> 00:28:40,750
They’re only a block away.

456
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:43,200
Well,

457
00:28:43,710 --> 00:28:45,860
we’ve settled down here for a while

458
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:48,640
and have registered our aliases.

459
00:28:48,640 --> 00:28:49,640
Don’t worry.

460
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:50,920
We’ll make sure of your safety.

461
00:28:54,190 --> 00:28:55,050
Who should we play?

462
00:28:58,470 --> 00:29:00,830
Father and two sons.

463
00:29:03,520 --> 00:29:04,400
Zichen,

464
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:06,110
hide yourself. I’ll be here.

465
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:07,880
Xie Yun...

466
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:10,070
If your father finds out about this,

467
00:29:10,070 --> 00:29:11,050
he’ll be furious.

468
00:29:11,760 --> 00:29:13,320
It won’t be a problem for me.

469
00:29:13,800 --> 00:29:14,590
But...

470
00:29:14,590 --> 00:29:17,310
Your Highness, Mr. Xie is right.

471
00:29:17,310 --> 00:29:19,220
You shouldn’t be here.

472
00:29:35,830 --> 00:29:37,470
You’re well-prepared!

473
00:29:38,230 --> 00:29:39,950
Xie Yun, I can explain.

474
00:29:40,560 --> 00:29:41,190
Enough.

475
00:29:41,760 --> 00:29:43,150
That can wait after the search.

476
00:29:49,640 --> 00:29:51,220
Your Highness, please.

477
00:30:06,190 --> 00:30:07,450
Have some food, girls.

478
00:30:08,560 --> 00:30:09,480
I’ve reheated

479
00:30:09,760 --> 00:30:11,070
the porridge on the stove.

480
00:30:11,070 --> 00:30:12,070
It’s warm enough to eat.

481
00:30:12,070 --> 00:30:13,250
Thank you, Mrs. Song.

482
00:30:15,710 --> 00:30:17,110
Miss Li.

483
00:30:17,110 --> 00:30:18,090
I’m not a Li.

484
00:30:19,430 --> 00:30:21,830
I know. My bad.

485
00:30:21,830 --> 00:30:23,260
You know,

486
00:30:23,590 --> 00:30:24,740
Ms. Duan

487
00:30:25,070 --> 00:30:26,680
has been muddleheaded for over a decade.

488
00:30:27,400 --> 00:30:30,470
She doesn’t know

489
00:30:30,470 --> 00:30:31,650
what she says or does.

490
00:30:32,070 --> 00:30:32,920
Please

491
00:30:32,920 --> 00:30:34,620
don’t mind her.

492
00:30:36,470 --> 00:30:37,520
With all due respect,

493
00:30:37,520 --> 00:30:39,470
she seems fine to me.

494
00:30:39,470 --> 00:30:42,760
Well, she isn’t totally insane.

495
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:44,710
Some days are better than others.

496
00:30:44,740 --> 00:30:46,650
Sometimes, she seems fine

497
00:30:47,070 --> 00:30:48,520
but things she suddenly recalls

498
00:30:49,470 --> 00:30:50,760
may set her off.

499
00:30:50,760 --> 00:30:52,420
Has Jiuniang always been like this?

500
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,470
Jiuniang?

501
00:30:54,470 --> 00:30:56,430
She said she’s Duan Jiuniang.

502
00:30:56,710 --> 00:30:57,730
Duan Jiuniang?

503
00:31:00,470 --> 00:31:01,590
Over the past two decades,

504
00:31:01,950 --> 00:31:04,920
the top masters are

505
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:08,230
the South and North Blades,
the Swordsman,

506
00:31:08,230 --> 00:31:11,310
Guanxi Yellow and Green Palm
and Penglai Immortal.

507
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:14,470
Speaking of which,

508
00:31:14,470 --> 00:31:16,880
I’ve met with Yellow and Green Palm,
Duan Jiuniang

509
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:18,680
a few times.

510
00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:19,740
Sadly,

511
00:31:20,310 --> 00:31:21,920
she’s been missing for over a decade.

512
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:24,020
No way.

513
00:31:25,310 --> 00:31:26,470
Would the legendary Duan Jiuniang

514
00:31:26,470 --> 00:31:28,070
degrade herself

515
00:31:28,070 --> 00:31:29,080
to a local official’s concubine,

516
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:32,760
not to mention
a crazy and unfavorable one?

517
00:31:34,110 --> 00:31:35,520
Calling her

518
00:31:35,520 --> 00:31:37,470
Empress Dowager
would be more convincing.

519
00:31:37,470 --> 00:31:39,280
How do you know

520
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:42,870
I’m not?

521
00:31:48,230 --> 00:31:49,700
Nice blade.

522
00:31:51,160 --> 00:31:51,940
Too bad, it’s broken.

523
00:31:54,310 --> 00:31:57,640
Is she really the one?

524
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:01,450
Finish your meal before going out.

525
00:32:03,590 --> 00:32:04,700
It’s dangerous outside.

526
00:32:05,350 --> 00:32:07,550
Watch out for the big bad wolf!

527
00:32:11,310 --> 00:32:12,590
Let’s go.

528
00:32:31,310 --> 00:32:33,470
Sorry for the trouble.

529
00:32:33,470 --> 00:32:34,230
I apologize.

530
00:32:34,230 --> 00:32:35,390
Good day. Take care.

531
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:45,190
Search it.

532
00:32:46,310 --> 00:32:47,260
-Officer.
-Come here.

533
00:33:06,350 --> 00:33:06,990
Who are you?

534
00:33:08,110 --> 00:33:10,110
Officer,

535
00:33:10,110 --> 00:33:13,070
I’m Liu San, 50 years old,

536
00:33:13,070 --> 00:33:14,680
a widower.

537
00:33:14,680 --> 00:33:17,350
I have two sons.

538
00:33:17,350 --> 00:33:19,040
We’re all farmers.

539
00:33:19,040 --> 00:33:22,760
The eldest one is Liu Shi,

540
00:33:22,760 --> 00:33:25,280
and the younger one is Liu Shan.

541
00:33:29,760 --> 00:33:30,520
Would you like some water?

542
00:33:30,520 --> 00:33:31,560
Let me get you some.

543
00:33:31,560 --> 00:33:32,640
Go away.

544
00:33:32,640 --> 00:33:34,110
Save it.

545
00:33:34,110 --> 00:33:35,460
Or I’ll get suspicious.

546
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,620
Those three are clean.

547
00:33:42,110 --> 00:33:43,320
Let’s go to the next one.

548
00:33:46,230 --> 00:33:48,060
Take care, Officer. Have a nice day.

549
00:33:59,590 --> 00:34:00,470
Who is it?

550
00:34:00,470 --> 00:34:02,230
Shi, Shi!

551
00:34:02,230 --> 00:34:03,450
I’m so sorry. I...

552
00:34:06,560 --> 00:34:07,330
I’m fine, Father.

553
00:34:46,520 --> 00:34:48,710
Why do farmers like you

554
00:34:48,710 --> 00:34:50,320
need a desk?

555
00:34:50,320 --> 00:34:51,760
Who

556
00:34:52,280 --> 00:34:54,150
is it for?

557
00:34:58,470 --> 00:34:59,670
Officer,

558
00:34:59,670 --> 00:35:01,670
I used to be a teacher

559
00:35:01,670 --> 00:35:04,190
and moved here to make a living.

560
00:35:44,670 --> 00:35:45,630
Shi!

561
00:35:49,080 --> 00:35:50,430
-Shi! Shi!
-Shi!

562
00:35:50,430 --> 00:35:51,630
-Are you alright?
-Shi!

563
00:35:51,630 --> 00:35:52,360
How do you feel, Shi?

564
00:35:52,360 --> 00:35:54,190
Officer, my son has the white plague.

565
00:35:54,190 --> 00:35:55,560
It’s almost incurable.

566
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:01,670
The white plague?

567
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:04,670
How did he get it?

568
00:36:04,670 --> 00:36:06,520
Refugees flooded into Huarong

569
00:36:06,520 --> 00:36:08,870
a while ago and broke the peace here.

570
00:36:08,870 --> 00:36:10,630
Many of them suffered from that disease

571
00:36:10,630 --> 00:36:12,750
and they must’ve infected my son.

572
00:36:13,230 --> 00:36:13,910
I... I...

573
00:36:13,910 --> 00:36:16,390
Please let him get treated first.

574
00:36:16,390 --> 00:36:17,000
Gross!

575
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:17,520
Officer.

576
00:36:17,520 --> 00:36:18,360
Let’s go!

577
00:36:20,190 --> 00:36:21,800
Officer.

578
00:36:22,670 --> 00:36:23,760
We’re losing him!

579
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:25,120
Shan,

580
00:36:25,120 --> 00:36:26,280
go get the physician!

581
00:36:26,280 --> 00:36:27,430
