while Blessed Dog

606
00:38:00,870 --> 00:38:03,040
is after Miss and Mr. Wu

607
00:38:03,040 --> 00:38:04,160
who escaped from the Inn.

608
00:38:06,230 --> 00:38:08,430
Obviously, Shen Tianshu is here

609
00:38:08,430 --> 00:38:10,910
for you.

610
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:25,740
Zichen,

611
00:38:26,230 --> 00:38:27,630
didn’t you see

612
00:38:27,630 --> 00:38:28,800
refugees in Huarong

613
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:30,080
outnumbered those elsewhere?

614
00:38:30,800 --> 00:38:32,300
They know this place is safe.

615
00:38:33,390 --> 00:38:34,020
Why?

616
00:38:37,080 --> 00:38:38,630
Xie Yun, I...

617
00:38:38,630 --> 00:38:39,950
Because you’re here.

618
00:38:43,320 --> 00:38:45,390
Huo Liantao must’ve ordered his men

619
00:38:45,390 --> 00:38:46,700
to not cause trouble in town.

620
00:38:47,800 --> 00:38:48,710
Yet here you are

621
00:38:48,710 --> 00:38:50,520
making yourself a target

622
00:38:50,520 --> 00:38:52,520
and thinking no one would find you.

623
00:38:52,520 --> 00:38:53,320
Xie Yun,

624
00:38:54,230 --> 00:38:55,420
I understand what you said.

625
00:38:56,760 --> 00:38:58,280
I came to Huarong

626
00:38:58,280 --> 00:38:59,040
simply to

627
00:38:59,040 --> 00:39:00,870
contact Huo Liantao in the first place.

628
00:39:01,840 --> 00:39:02,470
I didn’t know

629
00:39:02,470 --> 00:39:04,040
refugees would follow me here.

630
00:39:06,390 --> 00:39:09,120
Seeing them homeless

631
00:39:09,120 --> 00:39:10,710
and starving,

632
00:39:10,710 --> 00:39:12,340
I couldn’t sit and do nothing.

633
00:39:15,910 --> 00:39:17,060
So it was also you

634
00:39:17,430 --> 00:39:18,650
who gave them

635
00:39:19,520 --> 00:39:20,110
free food.

636
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:33,000
I knew that’d

637
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:34,380
get me into trouble,

638
00:39:34,950 --> 00:39:35,600
but I couldn’t turn a blind eye

639
00:39:35,600 --> 00:39:36,840
to those innocent people.

640
00:39:39,190 --> 00:39:40,570
I’m sorry that I dragged you into this.

641
00:39:41,800 --> 00:39:42,840
Zichen,

642
00:39:43,190 --> 00:39:45,230
I’m proud

643
00:39:45,230 --> 00:39:46,540
that you’d risk your life for others.

644
00:39:48,950 --> 00:39:50,080
But the problem is,

645
00:39:50,080 --> 00:39:52,120
although Shen Tianshu hasn’t found you,

646
00:39:52,120 --> 00:39:53,470
the fact is you’re caged.

647
00:39:53,470 --> 00:39:54,840
His men are searching door to door.

648
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:56,400
Two checkpoints are set up at the gate.

649
00:39:57,800 --> 00:39:59,180
Even if there were ways to get out,

650
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:02,370
Mr. Bai wouldn’t allow you
to take such a risk.

651
00:40:10,950 --> 00:40:11,910
What’s the use

652
00:40:11,910 --> 00:40:12,750
of caging me?

653
00:40:13,710 --> 00:40:15,630
What can he do about me?

654
00:40:15,630 --> 00:40:16,950
If he’s trying to use me

655
00:40:16,950 --> 00:40:18,390
to get Huo Liantao,

656
00:40:18,390 --> 00:40:19,440
that’s not going to happen.

657
00:40:20,430 --> 00:40:21,120
We aren’t

658
00:40:21,120 --> 00:40:22,430
that close.

659
