Right now, your troops

660
00:40:26,710 --> 00:40:28,470
are stationed at the border.

661
00:40:28,470 --> 00:40:29,360
They can get here

662
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:31,150
in seven or eight days.

663
00:40:31,150 --> 00:40:32,700
Hearing that you’re in trouble,

664
00:40:33,600 --> 00:40:34,700
even if your father knows
it could be a trap,

665
00:40:35,280 --> 00:40:36,940
he’ll definitely take action.

666
00:40:37,870 --> 00:40:39,800
But Shen Tianshu has no reason to do so.

667
00:40:40,120 --> 00:40:41,560
Demons Manor aside,

668
00:40:41,870 --> 00:40:43,430
what about Yu Wenzhi?

669
00:40:44,190 --> 00:40:45,230
If something happens to a prince

670
00:40:45,300 --> 00:40:46,750
in the enemy’s jurisdiction,

671
00:40:47,520 --> 00:40:49,440
won’t Yu Wenzhi make a fuss?

672
00:40:51,270 --> 00:40:51,930
Zichen,

673
00:40:52,710 --> 00:40:54,400
you’re too naive.

674
00:40:56,000 --> 00:40:56,720
Your Highness,

675
00:40:57,230 --> 00:40:59,150
I’ve told you to leave

676
00:40:59,150 --> 00:41:00,910
as soon as possible.

677
00:41:00,910 --> 00:41:03,200
Mr. Xie also thinks the same.

678
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:07,920
Now it isn’t a good time.

679
00:41:09,320 --> 00:41:11,600
Zichen, write a letter

680
00:41:11,600 --> 00:41:13,120
to Huo Liantao.

681
00:41:13,120 --> 00:41:15,500
Make sure Demons see it
delivered to Huo’s Manor.

682
