690
00:42:00,390 --> 00:42:01,350
Simple.

691
00:42:01,950 --> 00:42:04,600
Take ten moves from me first.

692
00:42:07,600 --> 00:42:08,850
But you can’t.

693
00:42:11,360 --> 00:42:12,580
My skills

694
00:42:12,950 --> 00:42:14,360
